Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: It's Been Hard Convincing Allies that it's War
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxbxl
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 13 Sep 2002
Alistair Cooke reflects on the anniversary of the September 11 attacks and considers a type of warfare so new that some European generals can't be convinced it is war at all.